OL,3,CNew website launched to show river
OL,4,Cpollution levels
OL,6,FWatch: ITV News Meridian's report by
OL,7,FNatalie Verney
OL,9,FA new website has been launched for
OL,10,Friver users in Oxfordshire which
OL,11,Fprovides up-to-date pollution levels.
OL,13,FIt's so people can make an informed
OL,14,Fchoice about getting in the water.
OL,16,FThe Oxford River Portal acts like a
OL,17,Fone-stop-shop by bringing data like
OL,18,Fwater levels, raw sewage spills, and
OL,19,Fwater quality measurements together to
OL,20,Fone place.
