OL,3,CNew website launched to show river
OL,4,Cpollution levels
OL,6,FPreviously this amount of data would
OL,7,Fbe available on different websites and
OL,8,Fdifficult to access.
OL,10,FUsers of the website can zoom in on a
OL,11,Fsingle map and click on any of more
OL,12,Fthan 2,000 locations to find out real-
OL,13,Ftime information or data from the past
OL,14,Fthree years.
OL,16,FIts launch follows increasing public
OL,17,Fconcern over the state of our rivers.
