OL,3,CNew website launched to show river
OL,4,Cpollution levels
OL,6,FWild swimming is popular at the two
OL,7,Fdesignated bathing sites in
OL,8,FOxfordshire - Port Meadow and
OL,9,FWallingford Beach.
OL,11,FThe website will make it quicker and
OL,12,Feasier for swimmers to check pollution
OL,13,Flevels and work out if it's safe
OL,14,Fenough to swim.
OL,16,F"We hope it can encourage people to
OL,17,Fuse their local waterways safely" -
OL,18,FClaire Robertson
