OL,3,CNew website launched to show river
OL,4,Cpollution levels
OL,6,FClaire Robertson, Oxford Rivers
OL,7,FProject Officer at Thames21, said:
OL,8,F"There has been a lot of stuff in the
OL,9,Fmedia, there is a lot of information
OL,10,Feverywhere, saying how polluted rivers
OL,11,Fare.
OL,13,F"Yes, rivers in this country are in
OL,14,Ftrouble, only 15% of them are in good
OL,15,Fecological health. However, not all of
OL,16,Fit is polluted all of the time,
OL,17,Fthey're very variable.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
