OL,3,CNew website launched to show river
OL,4,Cpollution levels
OL,6,F"There have been lots of times, for
OL,7,Finstance over this summer, where the
OL,8,Fbacteria levels at our local swimming
OL,9,Fsites have been below the threshold of
OL,10,Fconcern so we hope it can encourage
OL,11,Fpeople to use their local waterways
OL,12,Fsafely."
OL,14,FThe site has been set up Thames21,
OL,15,FRivers Trust, and the UK Centre for
OL,16,FEcology & Hydrology (UKCEH).
OL,18,FThey hope it will help the public use
OL,19,Fthe river safely, whilst also
OL,20,Fassisting academics and campaigners
OL,21,Fwith their river investigations.
